column2: Flag: Sample media is not water
column3: Flag: Result value is not numeric or result value is NA and no detection limit value is provided
column4: Flag: Conflict between detection condition text and detection limit type or detection limit type is not in WQX domain tables (likely USGS/NWIS-specific)
column5: Flag: Invalid speciation for associated characteristic
column6: Flag: Invalid characteristic and fraction combination
column7: Flag: Invalid units for a given characteristic and media combination
column8: Flag: Measurement activity type code indicates it is a QC replicate, duplicate, or blank
